702419f-a.title: Brooklyn: 5th Street (North) - Havemeyer Street
702419f-a.text:
North 5th Street, north side, at the intersection of Havemeyer Street
and Metropolitan Ave. Also seen is Havemeyer Street, east side, north from
North 5th Street. A view of St. Dominic Church and Rectory. (R.C.).
August 9, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
